name: "Venus Flytrap" by Sunny Crittenden (digital, 2019)
description: This is the 3rd digital drawing I ever did. It was created on a Samsung Galaxy tablet with the Adobe Draw app and an analog stylus on August 9th, 2019. Hallmark advice with a twist; in a world of herbivores, be a carnivore. I'm minting this on Hic Et Nunc on April 22nd, 2021, in honour of Earth Day, in an edition of 40.
